{"published time": "2024-03-16T02:01:47+08:00", "images": ["https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plenaria.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0286-1024x683.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faixa-e-bandeira-na-frente-do-evento-1024x680.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0284-683x1024.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plateia-do-evento-2-1-1024x702.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Fala-do-juiz-aposentado-Jorge-Moreno-relator-do-Tribunal-Popular-1024x680.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0494-1-683x1024.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Tribunal-testemunha-in-loco-as-destruicoes-promovidas-pelos-grileiros-1024x680.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0692-1024x683.jpg"], "content": "<div class=\"el-single-thumbnail\">\n <img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1121\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1688px) 100vw, 1688px\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plenaria.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plenaria.jpg\" width=\"1688\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n <p>\n  On March 9 and 10, the victorious Popular Court against grabbing and the landlord crimes was held in Vilela village in Junco do Maranh\u00e3o. The event was attended by popular lawyers, researchers, trade unionists and journalists from other regions of the country who participated in the court's judging committee.\n </p>\n <p>\n  The Court also had the participation of different organizations, such as the Union of Communities in Fight and the Student Collective Filhos do Povo, who organized students to attend the event. The peasant leadership\n  <a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/ma-luiz-vila-nova-memorias-da-vida-e-da-luta-de-um-militante-foi-relancado-em-evento-na-ufma/\">\n   Luiz Vila Nova\n  </a>\n  also attended the event.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171093\" data-id=\"171093\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"683\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0286-1024x683.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0286-1024x683.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Peasants extend track at the event. Photo: Database and\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171096\" data-id=\"171096\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"680\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faixa-e-bandeira-na-frente-do-evento-1024x680.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faixa-e-bandeira-na-frente-do-evento-1024x680.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Event entrance track announced the tone. Photo: Database and\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171089\" data-id=\"171089\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0284-683x1024.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0284-683x1024.jpg\" width=\"683\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Students took caravan to the event. Photo: Photo: Database and\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171094\" data-id=\"171094\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"702\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plateia-do-evento-2-1-1024x702.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plateia-do-evento-2-1-1024x702.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Palestinian flag was extended next to the central lane of the event. Photo: Database and\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  Throughout the auditorium, organizations flags and tracks with consigns of the land struggle decorated the environment. Right on the access road, a track\n  <strong>\n   Out land grabbers of our lands! By the title of our possessions!\n  </strong>\n  set the tone of the event. Inside the auditorium, other ranges condemned the grabbing, the large mining and called for the union of the peasants. The signatures were from squatters from different communities, such as Gleba Campina, Vilela village, Caranandeua and Jaraquara communities and the Association of Farmers of the village of Maracacura, the municipality of Carutapera.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171095\" data-id=\"171095\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"680\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Fala-do-juiz-aposentado-Jorge-Moreno-relator-do-Tribunal-Popular-1024x680.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Fala-do-juiz-aposentado-Jorge-Moreno-relator-do-Tribunal-Popular-1024x680.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Speaking of retired judge Jorge Moreno, rapporteur of the Popular Court. Photo: Database and\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171097\" data-id=\"171097\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0494-1-683x1024.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0494-1-683x1024.jpg\" width=\"683\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Peasant Leadership Luiz Vila Nova participated in the Popular Court. Photo: Database and\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  In one of the event's activities, the peasants organized a motorcycle caravan to visit the Gleba Campina and ascertain the crimes promoted by the land grabbers.\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171099\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"680\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Tribunal-testemunha-in-loco-as-destruicoes-promovidas-pelos-grileiros-1024x680.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Tribunal-testemunha-in-loco-as-destruicoes-promovidas-pelos-grileiros-1024x680.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Court witnesses on the spot the destruction promoted by the land grabbers. Photo: Database and\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n  As a referral from the Popular Court, the present organizations called a day of mobilization and fight against the Maranh\u00e3o State Grade Law to May 1st. The note can be read\n  <a href=\"https://medium.com/@comsolute/nota-conjunta-abaixo-a-lei-da-grilagem-35783ca1efa7\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">\n   in full here\n  </a>\n  .\n </p>\n <p>\n  In a joint statement, the Solidarity Committee for the Fight for Land (ComSolute) and the Union of Communities in Fighting (UCL) writes: \u201cThis is a victorious event in every way: to establish and unify a political agenda for the defense of rights. of the people; in producing legal material assistant to the cause of communities; in shaking those present around solidarity with the struggle for the land. \u201d\n </p>\n <p>\n  The note also makes a warm greeting to the student collective Filhos do Povo, who took a bus full of students. According to present, the Popular Court was a milestone in the development of the new student movement in Maranh\u00e3o.\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171092\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"683\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0692-1024x683.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0692-1024x683.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Participants celebrate during cultural activity. Photo: Database and\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n</div>\n", "source": "https://anovademocracia.com.br/tribunal-popular-junco-maranhao/", "type": "article", "title": "The Popular Court against Grade and Latifundium Crimes in Junco do Maranh\u00e3o - The New Democracy", "description": "The event was attended by popular lawyers, researchers, trade unionists and journalists from other regions of the country who participated in the court's judging committee.", "modified time": "2024-03-15T15:22:11-03:00", "updated time": "2024-03-15T15:22:11-03:00", "author": ["Comit\u00ea de Apoio \u2013 S\u00e3o Lu\u00eds (MA)"], "categories": ["Luta Pela Terra"], "tags": ["grilagem", "Pistolagem"], "sections": ["Luta Pela Terra"], "link-section": "luta-pela-terra", "source_name": "A Nova Democracia"}